空間分析 作業十

電機四 B05901013 張景皓

6/3/2020

村里學校總數

lm.palette <- colorRampPalette(c( "white","orange","red"), space = "rgb")
spplot(Tainan_li, zcol="SCHOOL_COUNT", col.regions=lm.palette(20))

Local Moran

LISA <- localmoran(Tainan_li$SCHOOL_COUNT, Tainan_li.nb.w, zero.policy = T, alternative = "two.sided")

diff <- Tainan_li$SCHOOL_COUNT - mean(Tainan_li$SCHOOL_COUNT)
z <- LISA[, 4]

quad <- c() #don't use vector
quad[diff > 0 & z > 0] <- 1 #H-H
quad[diff < 0 & z > 0] <- 2 #L-L
quad[diff > 0 & z < 0] <- 3 #H-L
quad[diff < 0 & z < 0] <- 4 #L-H
quad[LISA[, 5] > 0.05] <- 5

color <- c("red", "blue", "lightpink", "lightblue", "grey", rgb(0.95, 0.95, 0.95))
plot(Tainan_li, border = "grey", col = color[quad], main = "LISA Map")
legend("bottomleft", legend = c("HH", "LL", "HL", "LH", "NS"), fill = color, bty = "n", y.intersp = 1, x.intersp = 1)

Gi*

Tainan_li.nb.in <- include.self(Tainan_li.nb)
Tainan_li.nb.w.in <- nb2listw(Tainan_li.nb.in)
Gi <- localG(Tainan_li$SCHOOL_COUNT, Tainan_li.nb.w.in)
LG <- as.vector(Gi)

quad <- c()
quad[LG >= 1.645] = 1 #cluster
quad[LG < 1.645] = 2 #non-cluster

color <- c("red", "grey")
plot(Tainan_li, border = "grey", col = color[quad], main = "Cluster Map")
legend("bottomleft", c("Cluster", "Non-cluster"), fill = color, bty = "n", y.intersp = 1, x.intersp = 1)
